subject: Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Center Jared Berggren scored Wisconsin’s final 5 points and the 16th-ranked Badgers beat No. 8 Ohio State, 63-60, on Sunday, assuring Michigan State of at least a share of the Big Ten title.
